Sentencas: In this paper we report an investigation of proton conduction in two gallate systems, La1-xBa1+xGaO4-x/2 and La1-xSr2+xGaO5-x/2, containing tetrahedral Ga.
Titulo: Investigation of proton conduction in La1-xBa1+xGaO4-x/2 and La1-xSr2+xGaO5-x/2

Sentencas: Measurements in dry atmospheres show that both systems exhibit a p-type contribution to the conductivity, while a comparison between dry and wet atmospheres shows evidence for proton conduction.
Titulo: Investigation of proton conduction in La1-xBa1+xGaO4-x/2 and La1-xSr2+xGaO5-x/2

Sentencas: The La1-xBa1+xGaO4-x/2 system shows the highest proton conductivities, with conductivities reported being significantly higher (approximate to 1 X 10(-4)
Titulo: Investigation of proton conduction in La1-xBa1+xGaO4-x/2 and La1-xSr2+xGaO5-x/2
